content: Hi, I spoke with a MI voter this afternoon who already voted. I politely asked who they were voting for, but they did not disclose and hung up. What canvass result should I use?

If it was the correct person, I would suggest... 

First click the "correct person" button.  On the next screen click "undecided/other/not voting"
let me know if that works for you
Thanks! That is what I selected.
